%% PG Discovery Platform — Enquiry Submission Flow
%% Visitor journey from browse to enquiry confirmation

flowchart LR
    A[Visitor] -->|Browses PGs| B[Public Listing Page]
    B -->|Clicks PG| C[PG Detail Page]
    C -->|Fills Enquiry Form| D[Route Handler]
    D -->|Validate with Zod| E{Valid?}
    E -->|No| F[Return Error]
    E -->|Yes| G{Anti-Spam Check<br/>1 per phone/PG/24h}
    G -->|Violation| H[Reject Duplicate]
    G -->|Pass| I[Insert into DB]
    I --> J[Send Confirmation Email<br/>via MJML Template]
    J --> K[Owner Notified via Email]
    K --> L[Owner Updates Status:<br/>New → Contacted → Closed]
